Recommends: python3-pyaudio, python3-pynput
Description: Voice-to-text daemon for Linux using OpenAI Whisper
 Whisper Voice Daemon is a professional voice input system that runs as a
 background service and transcribes speech to text using OpenAI's Whisper
 model.
 .
 Features:
  * Global hotkey support (Ctrl+Alt+V)
  * 100% local processing (privacy-first)
  * Voice Activity Detection (VAD)
  * Manual control (stop/cancel)
  * Bilingual interface (English/Portuguese)
  * Systemd integration with auto-start
  * Works everywhere (terminal, browser, IDE)
